docs/testing/verify-matrix.md:37:| FILE-STORAGE-ERROR-MAPPING-001 | FR-003 / FR-006 / AC-E005 / AC-E026 | repaired | `npm run test:file` 覆盖 object storage put/read/publish 失败均映射为 `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR`、不生成可下载 metadata，并通过 scheduler 断言任务最终 `FAILED + FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` | production-equivalent adapter + local/Docker MySQL；不声明 live OSS/S3 |
docs/testing/verify-matrix.md:38:| FILE-RENDER-ERROR-CONTRACT-REPAIR-001 | FR-006 / AC-E027 | repaired | `npm run test:file` 覆盖 XLSX 与 ZIP renderer 失败在 object storage 写入前映射为 `EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR`、写入 `PACKAGE_FAILED` 事件中的 `renderInputSummary` 和 `failureReason`、不生成可下载 metadata，并通过 scheduler 断言任务最终 `FAILED + EXPORT_RENDER_ERROR` 审计；同一命令继续覆盖 object storage put/read/publish 失败保持 `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` | local/Docker MySQL + 本地 object storage mock / production-equivalent adapter；不声明 live OSS/S3 |
docs/testing/verify-matrix.md:48:| TASK-CANCEL-ATOMICITY-001 | FR-012 / AC-012 / AC-E015 | repaired | `npm run test:api` 断言取消状态更新必须携带原 `status` 与 `attemptNo` CAS 条件，旧 PENDING 取消快照不能覆盖已推进到 EXECUTING 的任务；`npm run test:worker` 断言旧 EXECUTING 取消快照不能覆盖 FAILED retry 后递增出的新 `attemptNo`。同一轮继续保留 PENDING cancel、EXECUTING 批次边界 cancel 与 FAILED retry 既有状态机证据 | local/Docker MySQL API + worker evidence；CAS miss 收口为未更新或非法状态，不声明外部生产 MySQL evidence |
docs/testing/verify-matrix.md:49:| DEFAULT-QUERY-RETRY-ALIGNMENT-001 | FR-006 / FR-010 / AC-020 / AC-E004 / AC-E020 | repaired | `npm run test:worker` 断言 scheduler 未显式传入 `maxQueryBatchRetries` 时默认允许 3 次 query batch retry checkpoint，第四次失败才收口为 `FAILED + QUERY_EXECUTION_ERROR`；既有 `maxQueryBatchRetries: 1` worker 用例继续证明显式 override 生效，backoff checkpoint 与最终失败审计不回归 | local/Docker MySQL worker evidence；默认值来源对齐 `docs/product/state-matrix.yaml` 的 `query_batch_max_retries: 3`，不声明外部 datasource live evidence |
docs/testing/verify-matrix.md:50:| PUBLIC-ERROR-REDACTION-001 | FR-010 / AC-010 / AC-E012 / AC-E013 | repaired | `npm run test:api` 断言 `sendError` 对 `ApiError` 和未知 `Error` 均按公开 `errorCode` 返回安全消息，任务详情 `errorMessage` 从 `errorCode` 派生且不回显 datasource credential 文本；`npm run test:query` 覆盖 datasource adapter 与 SQL 执行异常收口，不泄露 SQL、密码或 secret；`npm run test:file` 覆盖 object storage put/read/publish 失败统一返回安全 `FILE_VERIFY_ERROR` 文本；`npm run test:contract` 守护 OpenAPI 对公开错误消息与任务失败摘要的脱敏约束 | local/Docker MySQL API + query + file + contract evidence；审计 `errorCode`、公开 `errorCode` 和既有 FAILED 状态语义保持不变；不声明外部业务数据源或 live OSS/S3 evidence |
